I do, I do.

51
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:04,760
I do.

52
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,510
Oh, my silly head.

53
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:23,480
When I was talking to you,

54
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,230
I put some salt in twice.

55
00:06:24,350 --> 00:06:25,270
Oh, what the heck!

56
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,880
When someone gets old, she just...

57
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:28,040
Have some fish.

58
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,000
I tasted it. It's OK.

59
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,350
Come on.

60
00:06:29,550 --> 00:06:29,790
Taste some.

61
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:30,480
I'll get it myself.

62
00:06:30,550 --> 00:06:30,950
Eat.

63
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:35,880
Eat.

64
