Meisu!

189
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:39,550
Meisu!

190
00:16:44,350 --> 00:16:45,200
Meisu!

191
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:54,150
Meisu!

192
00:16:55,110 --> 00:16:55,880
Meisu!

193
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:57,710
Meisu!

194
00:17:00,350 --> 00:17:01,000
Meisu!

195
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:03,030
Meisu!

196
00:17:04,070 --> 00:17:04,830
Meisu!

197
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:06,920
Meisu!

198
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:09,040
Meisu!

199
00:17:10,830 --> 00:17:12,230
Help!

200
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:14,760
Somebody help!

201
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:17,280
Meisu.

202
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,230
Meisu, please don't.

203
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,350
Meisu.

204
00:17:23,430 --> 00:17:24,520
Meisu, I'm sorry.

205
00:17:28,950 --> 00:17:30,800
Help!

206
