Wang Yang. Relationship.

212
00:17:58,800 --> 00:17:59,470
Father and son.

213
00:18:26,340 --> 00:18:29,820
(Luo Meisu, Wang Yang)

214
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:38,880
Gong Biao's family.

215
00:18:41,710 --> 00:18:43,110
She's arriving soon, I guess.

216
00:18:43,110 --> 00:18:44,950
I... I'll rush her.

217
00:18:44,950 --> 00:18:46,000
Hurry up.

218
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:53,760
Wang.

219
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:57,350
I got to the wrong place.

220
00:18:57,350 --> 00:18:58,520
I went back there.

221
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:00,280
Where's Biao?

222
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:01,110
In there.

223
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,000
He's dressed.

224
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,040
How about you take a look at him?

225
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:09,920
I brought some cosmetics
to give him some makeup.

226
00:19:10,950 --> 00:19:12,400
I'd be worried if someone else did.

227
00:19:13,560 --> 00:19:15,280
I'll tell them about it.

228
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:17,160
Excuse me, sir.

229
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:21,710
Gong Biao's wife has come.

230
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:24,950
She wants to check on him
and give him some makeup.

231
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:27,430
Come in, then.

232
00:19:27,430 --> 00:19:28,400
But don't stay there too long.

233
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:28,880
OK, OK.

234
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:29,880
OK. Thank you.

235
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,680
How about I get in, too?

236
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:32,560
Don't bother, Wang.

237
00:19:32,560 --> 00:19:33,310
I...

238
00:19:33,800 --> 00:19:35,560
I want some time with him alone.

239
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:39,660
(Let the dead rest in peace.
Please be quiet.)

240
00:20:58,310 --> 00:20:59,000
Biao,

241
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:02,880
I'm not gonna cry today.

242
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:09,230
Or you would feel sorry.

243
00:21:14,470 --> 00:21:15,830
You love the smiling me, right?

244
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:22,070
I'll smile, then.

245
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:51,430
These days, I was thinking.

246
00:21:56,800 --> 00:22:00,430
You and I didn't have a very happy life.

247
00:22:03,590 --> 00:22:04,760
Why?

248
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,590
I can't figure it out.

249
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:15,640
I want to ask you.

250
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,560
How about
we have another try in the next life?

251
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,310
What do you say?

252
00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:45,160
What about this?

253
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,190
Red sandalwood made in China.

254
00:22:46,190 --> 00:22:47,640
The price is good. 2,500 yuan.

255
00:22:50,230 --> 00:22:51,350
A little bit old-fashioned.

256
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:54,310
How much is this one?

257
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:55,520
A bit more expensive. 4,000 yuan.

258
00:22:55,520 --> 00:22:56,800
Made of Indian red sandalwood.

259
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:58,520
I'll take this one.

260
00:23:03,310 --> 00:23:04,560
The wood is very good.

261
00:23:05,280 --> 00:23:06,640
It would never be broken.

262
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:07,520
Look.

263
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:08,560
You can even put a photo here.

264
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:10,760
Have you brought his photo?

265
00:23:10,760 --> 00:23:11,880
I can put it in for you.

266
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:15,070
I have to search his flat for a photo.

267
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:16,920
How about this?

268
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:18,590
I'll pay for it first.

269
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:20,560
And then, you keep this for me.

270
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:22,000
Sure. Turn left and pay in the lobby.

271
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,520
OK.

272
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:32,190
Excuse me, do you have scissors?

273
00:23:33,040 --> 00:23:33,560
Yes.

274
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:47,060
(Certificate of Hualin Taxi Driver
Name: Gong Biao)

275
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:53,880
Biao, you made sense.

276
00:23:58,230 --> 00:24:02,280
Every one of us should be happy, right?

277
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:44,680
You're awake?

278
00:24:57,470 --> 00:24:58,710
Where are the words?

279
00:24:58,710 --> 00:24:59,520
What words?

280
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,280
Words.

281
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:03,400
The words.

282
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:04,350
What words?

283
00:25:05,070 --> 00:25:06,040
Gong Hui
[*Labor Union].

284
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,190
What labor union?

285
00:25:08,710 --> 00:25:09,830
Whose is this?

286
00:25:09,830 --> 00:25:11,160
The hospital's.

287
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:13,040
Hands off me!

288
